Package: rcli
Title: Addons for the R Command-Line Interface
Imports:
    utils,
    R.utils
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Henrik", family = "Bengtsson",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "henrikb@braju.com")
Description: By calling the API of this package during the R startup, in an Rprofile file, one can add extra features to the R command-line interface (CLI).  For example, rcli::r_cmd_call() will add CLI option '--flavor=<name>' to 'R CMD build' and 'R CMD check'.
